{"tid":1600010,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"華為 Mate 30 拍攝比 iPhone 好？因為發佈會造馬了！","createTime":"2019-09-28T11:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T14:14:39.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"20f1ed3b68e7c9df9560f8f7285ad743f8dd2c87","tid":1600010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T11:49:34.000Z","msg":"華為昨日正式發表全新的華為 Mate 30 Pro ，雖然未能支援 Google 服務及程式，不過華為就以Leica 四主鏡頭作賣點。而在發佈會之中，華為更不斷以 Mate 30 Pro 與蘋果最新的 iPhone 11 Pro Max 作比較，強調拍攝功能比對方更強。<br />\n不過為什麼華為會這麼肯定 Mate 30 Pro 比 iPhone 11 Pro Max 拍攝力更強？因為比較造馬了呀！華為於發佈會上，展示兩者於低光及背光的環境下拍攝作比較，不過有網民就發現多張比較相片都明顯出現問題。正如上圖所見，右邊 Mate 30 Pro 拍照時，女模特兒明顯有一個來自強光打燈形成的影子，與左面 iPhone 拍攝時光源來自模特兒身後明顥不同。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.android-hk.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/huawei_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.android-hk.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2Fhuawei_4.jpg&h=73557400&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除此之外，於低光自拍的比較中，亦不難發現 Mate 30 自拍時模特兒明顯有打燈輔助。果然華為都離不開中國公司的傳統文化，有興趣的朋友亦可以看看整個華為發佈會。"},{"pid":"fcea542a12d223f0e49353185ca8fd0e44f0866f","tid":1600010,"uid":263133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T11:52:24.000Z","msg":"支拿就是頭腦簡單"},{"pid":"51883b16e6cec0606763be696605376ff05f7d6d","tid":1600010,"uid":140552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T12:02:01.000Z","msg":"支那人唔造假先係新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7907c9876434281d5b5f85db9380d23995fa84ac","tid":1600010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T12:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c11d5c77fcda1f2999b847411f2a5d12a50e04","tid":1600010,"uid":90076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T13:07:50.000Z","msg":"不意外"},{"pid":"4d0986c5862aa7d7ec2380c4bdf71a025056d08d","tid":1600010,"uid":61545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T13:19:52.000Z","msg":"倒不如覺得iphone影得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d22f51944cae0ebd7e0fb556837dc4c3c2315e","tid":1600010,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"51883b16e6cec0606763be696605376ff05f7d6d","tid":1600010,"uid":140552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T12:02:01.000Z","msg":"支那人唔造假先係新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T14:14:39.000Z","msg":"造假係共產中文，係造馬"}]}